<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - Pet Care</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
  <style>
    /* Reduce spacing */
    main {
      padding-top: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .lead {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .nav-pills .nav-link {
      padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .accordion-button {
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .accordion-body {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .accordion-item {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem; /* reduce gap between sections */
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Privacy Policy' }) %>

  <main class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h1 class="fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted mb-2">Last updated: January 1, 2024</p>
      <p class="lead">We value your privacy. Hereâ€™s a clear breakdown of how we handle your data:</p>
    </div>

 

    <!-- Accordion Sections -->
    <div class="accordion" id="privacyAccordion">
      <div class="accordion-item" id="collect">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseCollect">
            1. Information We Collect
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseCollect" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>We may collect personal details you provide such as your name, email, and pet information. 
            We also track usage data such as schedules, health tracking, and community interactions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="storage">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseStorage">
            2. How Your Data Is Stored
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseStorage" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Data is securely stored in our database.</li>
              <li>Passwords are <strong>hashed and salted</strong> (bcrypt).</li>
              <li>We use HTTPS encryption to protect your information in transit.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="usage">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseUsage">
            3. How We Use Your Data
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseUsage" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Enable you to manage your account and pets.</li>
              <li>Improve services and add new features.</li>
              <li>Send updates and provide support.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="sharing">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSharing">
            4. Sharing of Information
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseSharing" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>We <strong>do not sell</strong> your personal data.  
            Limited sharing may occur with trusted providers (e.g., hosting, email) strictly to run the platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="rights">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseRights">
            5. Your Rights
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseRights" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Access and update your data anytime.</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your account.</li>
              <li>Manage notification and email preferences.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="retention">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseRetention">
            6. Data Retention
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseRetention" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Your data is stored while your account is active.  
            If deleted, data is permanently removed except where legally required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-item" id="contact">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseContact">
            7. Contact Us
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseContact" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#privacyAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>If you have questions, email us at  
              <a href="mailto:support@petcare.com">support@petcare.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
